result.name: Zero One Coffee & Roastery

reviews.text: Coffee was very good and strong. Try their oatly milk latte. Decor was very chic with minimal space for seating. Their iced chai latte was sweet and with a distinct cardamom flavour.
Decent place to chill with friends and for a cup of coffee
Very nice coffee at reasonable price, although the coffee size is a bit small.

Good coffee, arrogant staff, despite their young age. I asked for a little extra more milk and was asked to wait until three more customers were served. I'm not asking for any special treatment, just minimal sympathy.
Perfect place to relax within the busy environment in central, chill with a very good cappuccino with oat milk. Staffs are very friendly indeed.
